{"tid":1473580,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［社會福利］ 暴力及執法傷亡賠償計劃","createTime":"2019-08-15T01:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T06:32:33.000Z","uid":9230,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a50ecfa949958dfe7da6f7277a512796b173038","tid":1473580,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:34:54.000Z","msg":"暴力及執法傷亡賠償計劃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這項計劃目的是提供經濟援助給因暴力罪行或<span style=\"color: red;\">因執法人員使用武器執行職務﹐以致受傷的人士</span>或這些人士的受養人(如受害人因傷死亡)。此計劃無須供款﹐<span style=\"color: red;\">申請人亦無須接受經濟狀況調查</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05hDhsS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05hDhsS.png&h=01db9964&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M7szAey.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM7szAey.png&h=3fa0aba6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"980ed5a2ab55958cc6507ce639d58762bf8aff86","tid":1473580,"uid":127269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:35:42.000Z","msg":"好野梗係要推 claim得一蚊得一蚊"},{"pid":"c17c62eb66fce8db18e47f77a51c8620fb7c1c1f","tid":1473580,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:37:12.000Z","msg":"無辜辜食咗煙，又喉嚨不舒服超過3日，諗吓問政府拎返多少駛吓"},{"pid":"6a0c6e8c5b24d27952e3f8b64ff979b6bfd06c63","tid":1473580,"uid":63258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ede4f2cc6891a3a013dd84ebd925be37f167ab","tid":1473580,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6537fa3c0affe0ab2efc7afd035